                <div className="w-12 h-12 bg-white text-indigo-900 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black shadow-lg">2</div>
                <h3 className="text-xl font-black uppercase">Publish Website (Cloudflare)</h3>
                <ol className="text-sm text-indigo-200 space-y-4 list-decimal ml-4 font-medium">
                   <li>Buat akun <a href="https://dash.cloudflare.com" target="_blank" className="text-white underline">Cloudflare</a>.</li>
                   <li>Pilih <span className="text-white font-bold">Workers & Pages</span> -> <span className="text-white font-bold">Pages</span>.</li>
                   <li>Hubungkan ke GitHub repo Anda.</li>
                   <li>Masukkan <span className="text-white font-bold">Environment Variables</span> ini:</li>
                </ol>
                <div className="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 space-y-4 border border-white/10">
                   <div className="flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest">
                      <span>SUPABASE_URL</span>
                      <span className="text-green-400">OK</span>
                   </div>
                   <div className="h-px bg-white/10" />
                   <div className="flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest">
                      <span>SUPABASE_ANON_KEY</span>
                      <span className="text-green-400">OK</span>
